commit message: Added some more text on OSMOSE bugs.

Some more screenshots for the docs

Merge pull request #376 from johnjohndoe/typo-in-contributors

Fix typo in contributor name.
Define compatible Java version so Lint emits correct reports.

Define compatible Java version so Lint emits correct reports.

Fix issues with no place holder icon being generated and as a result no
button being displayed for preset items without an 'icon' attribute.

Updated translations, display the correct element id for reference OSM
objects in OSOMOSE bugs and display the bug id itself.
Improve debugging and be more robust wrt corrupt data
Updated reference in release note to master branch

Point out if that you are getting the same error more than once you
sould open an issue.
And more updates to the introduction.
Added extension to python markdown for generating the on device docs, re-converted all en markdown files.

Completed German translation of the introduction doc, lots of
improvements of the original.
Yet another update of the generated html files
Added a version indication to the web pages.

De-select elements when returning from property editor in tag editing
mode.

Documentation, preset and translations updates, fix tag editing mode
regression.
